da."},{"id":"en_GB","ocurrence":0,"type":"STRING","value":"100% percale cotton children's bedlinen set which reinvents the classic gingham print, available in a wide variety of colours so you can combine it with any style of bedroom. If you choose one of the more intense colours, it will help give a distinctive look to a room transitioning from a child's to a young person's bedroom."},{"id":"en_GB","ocurrence":1,"type":"STRING","value":"The 200-thread-count provides a highly agreeable, comfortable texture which, together with the cotton, gives it softness and creates a delightful feeling on contact with the skin. The natural fibres also help to generate uniform heat while letting out the moisture created while asleep, so the bed constantly feels fresh."},{"id":"en_GB","ocurrence":2,"type":"STRING","value":"The set contains a top sheet and a pillow case."},{"id":"fr_FR","ocurrence":0,"type":"STRING","value":"Parure de lit pour enfant en percale de coton qui réinvente le grand classique de l'imprimé vichy dans une large palette de couleurs permettant de l'assortir à tous les styles de chambres. Des couleurs plus intenses vous aideront à apporter une petite touche différente à une chambre d'enfant devenue chambre d'adolescent."},{"id":"fr_FR","ocurrence":1,"type":"STRING","value":"Son coton 200 fils lui donne une texture très agréable et confortable pour plus de douceur au toucher. Ses fibres naturelles maintiennent une chaleur uniforme tout en permettant l'évacuation de l'humidité  et procurent ainsi une sensation de fraîcheur."},{"id":"fr_FR","ocurrence":2,"type":"STRING","value":"L'ensemble se compose d'un drap de dessus et d'une taie d'oreiller."}]}]},{"id":"GestionComprasStock","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"Calificacion1","type":"STRING","value":"A"},{"id":"Calificacion2","type":"STRING","value":"O"},{"id":"Calificacion4","type":"STRING","value":"VV"},{"id":"Calificacion5","type":"STRING","value":"AF"},{"id":"TipoDeGestion","type":"STRING","value":"06"}]},{